Class IndexREST

    public class IndexREST
extends java.lang.Object
implements Index
    Implementation of Index that uses ElasticSearch's REST interface to manipulate an index.

        public void saveObjects(java.lang.String type,
                        java.util.List<?> objs,
                        java.util.List<java.lang.String> ids,
                        java.util.List<java.lang.String> parentIds)
        Description copied from interface: Index
        Adds multiple objects to the index, presumably using ElasticSearch's bulk processing capabilities.

        saveObjects in interface Index
        Parameters:
        type - The type of the document
        objs - The objects to add
